      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AARIELLA'S GIRL (7) is a fast dog well performed over the sprint races. Was too tough when scoring last time over 340m at Hobart in a Grade 5 (19.25). Has an impeccable record here at this journey. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Can measure up again. SCOOBY DANGER (1) missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a Grade 6 three back before a placing at Hobart the following run. Can feature with the right run. WHERE'S AUNTY (8) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth at Hobart, but was among the placings at Hobart three back. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. SHERWOOD BOYS (3) deserves plenty of thought over this journey.",
